{"questionId":"14509306","questionHtml":"<div class=\"qb-parent-stem\"><p>Daniela wins a prize. She is offered two options for receiving her winnings over a period of three years.</p>\n<p>Option A: Daniela receives $4200 at the end of each month.</p>\n<p>Option B: Daniela receives $1500 at the end of the first month. Each month after this, the amount she receives increases by 4%.</p></div>\n<p>Option A;</p>","markschemeHtml":"<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>4200</mn><mo>×</mo><mn>36</mn></math>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <em><strong>(A1)</strong></em></p>\n<p><em><strong><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mo>=</mo><mn>151200</mn></math></strong></em></p>\n<p><em><strong><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mo>=</mo><mfenced><mo>$</mo></mfenced><mn>151000</mn></math>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; A1</strong></em></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:right;\"><em><strong>[2 marks]</strong></em></p>","meta":{"questionId":"14509306","referenceCode":"23N.2.SL.TZ1.8ai","subjectId":"50-dp-mathematics-analysis-and-approaches","title":"Option A;","paper":"2","level":"SL","questionNumber":"i","marksAvailable":"[Maximum mark: 2]","breadcrumbLabels":["Topic 1—Number and algebra","Topic 1—Number and algebra","SL 1.3—Geometric sequences and series"],"memberSectionIds":[],"sectionOrders":{}},"schemaVersion":3}
